CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 4, 1961, pg. 22 reads: "The Marquettes - Members of the Marquettes Social Club celebrated their 10th anniversary with a gay party at Loendi Club recently. The speaker for the event was MRs. Hazel Garland of The Pittsburgh Courier.  Left to right, seated: Mmes. Doris Summers, Bernice Lucas, Hazel Garland, Juanita Hood, president; Berthenia Grant and Charlotte Moore.  Standing: Mmes. Martha Lucke, Ann Jones, Elizabeth Diggs, Betty Wysong, Dorothy Kellum and Irma Johnson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Marquettes Social Club members, seated from left: Doris Summers, Bernice Lucas, Hazel Garland, Juanita Hood, Berthenia Grant, and Charlotte Moore; standing: Martha Lucke, Ann Jones, Elizabeth Diggs, Betty Wysong, Dorothy Kellum, and Irma Johnson, gathered at banquet table in Loendi Club for 10th Anniversary
